comment: /**  * The name of the header or query parameter to be used.  */
code: /**  * The name of the header or query parameter to be used.  */ public void setName(String name) {     this.name = name. }

comment: /**  * To use header as the location of the API key.  */
code: /**  * To use header as the location of the API key.  */ public void setInHeader(Boolean inHeader) {     this.inHeader = inHeader. }

comment: /**  * To use query parameter as the location of the API key.  */
code: /**  * To use query parameter as the location of the API key.  */ public void setInQuery(Boolean inQuery) {     this.inQuery = inQuery. }
public RestSecurityApiKey withHeader(String name) {     setName(name).     setInHeader(true).     setInQuery(false).     return this. }
public RestSecurityApiKey withQuery(String name) {     setName(name).     setInQuery(true).     setInHeader(false).     return this. }
